'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 20''' was the 20th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', published for [[May]]/[[June]] [[1999]]. It was released with two covers, featuring [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] and [[Darth Maul/Legends|Darth Maul]], and reprinted material from [[Star Wars Insider 43|''Star Wars Insider'' 43]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Feel the Force]]
*[[Prequel Update]]: The Characters of Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'' {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 43}}
*[[Model Universe]]
*[[In the Star Wars Universe|In the ''Star Wars'' Universe]] &mdash; [[Dermot Crowley]] {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 41|''Star Wars Insider'' 41]]}}
*[[Prequel Profile]] &mdash; [[David Tattersall]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 43}}
*[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]
*[[Star Wars Q&A|Q&A]]

