*"[[George Lucas Down Under]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 43|''Star Wars Insider'' 43]]}}
*"[[Brian Blessed: A Blessed Event]]" (retitled "Boss Man") {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 43}}
*"[[Droids of Episode I]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 43}}
*"[[Lucasfilm Lifers]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 43}}
*Excerpt from ''[[Star Wars: The Action Figure Archive]]''.

